Come make the best smelling holiday simmer pot with me! Your whole house will smell like Christmas 🎄

All you need is:
1 orange
1 lemon 
1 cup or so of cranberries 
2 rosemary sprigs
A handful of whole cloves
Cinnamon sticks 
6 cups of water 
A dash of vanilla extract (adds so much!)
Bring to a simmer and add water as the day goes! 

Optional: apple slices, apple juice instead of water 

#holidays #simmerpot #christmasiscoming #smellssogood
